item.title: Pictures from FAB Fest
item.dc:creator: Brian Kirsten
item.content:encoded: For those of you who don't know me, I love beer, so we' ve been planning on attending this big beer/food festival thing in the heart of Miami (Bayfront Park). We ended up heading over to FAB Festival last Saturday. Here's are some pictures that Christine took.
